title: Coheed and Cambria - The Afterman: Ascension // Big Beige Demos
description:
Coheed and Cambria released The Afterman: Ascension in 2012. Following the initial release, the band opted to provide a special edition vinyl pressing of the demos they had created for The Afterman: Ascension & Descension. Subsequently, each release was only pressed on vinyl for special Record Store Day releases.

This particular vinyl rip is a true 24-bit lossless file from the original vinyl.

The method used was through a Technics SL-1200 MK2 >> Stock Tone Arm >> SHURE M44-7 Cartridge >> SHURE N447 needle >> Realistic Pre-AMP >> M-Audio Fast Track Pro >> Reaper FM audio encoder.
